  - m_Id: 52377073233920
    m_Localized: Turbo Turtle Abilities
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 70555631366144
    m_Localized: "Hide, survive, \nand outlast the turtle"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 70715996385280
    m_Localized: Destroy the flowers before the battery dies
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 71383066882048
    m_Localized: Return
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 71684834471936
    m_Localized: Energy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 71950996615168
    m_Localized: Revive
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8515446984433664
    m_Localized: Bringing a Flower Back to Life
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8513540824260608
    m_Localized: Turbo Turtle loses battery over time and when using its powers.
      Suns collected let it stay alive and avoid running out of power!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73353655758848
    m_Localized: "With 3 Suns, a player can bring back a defeated flower \nby getting
      close and holding the revive button."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75096028360704
    m_Localized: Flowers
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75140752224256
    m_Localized: Turtle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75882380668928
    m_Localized: Use your ability
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76195443519488
    m_Localized: Hide underground
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76557936242688
    m_Localized: Hold to revive an ally
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76675859099648
    m_Localized: Dash (hold and release)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76929119563776
    m_Localized: Bite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 77163023314944
    m_Localized: Turbo (hold)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 77746409058304
    m_Localized: Mine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 89166299279360
    m_Localized: 'Turbo Turtle stretches its neck to bite enemy Flowers.

      Uses
      a bit of battery

      (<sprite index=34>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 402636848771072
    m_Localized: Movement
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 411050282856448
    m_Localized: bite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 413542014005248
    m_Localized: dash
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 413586914029568
    m_Localized: mine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 414699897761792
    m_Localized: Spinning Charge
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 414978265329664
    m_Localized: Bite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 415292838129664
    m_Localized: Expensive Boost
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 415614163759104
    m_Localized: Detection Scan
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 416222107152384
    m_Localized: Electric Mine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 417629656854528
    m_Localized: 'Turbo Turtle curls into its shell and spins in place, then bursts
      forward when the button is released.

      Level 1: 1s charge

      Level
      2: 1.5s charge (can break some obstacles and stun the Flowers it hits).

      (hold
      <sprite index=33> + <sprite index=15> to aim, then release)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 417752331857920
    m_Localized: 'Turbo Turtle''s reactors overheat, granting increased speed but
      draining a lot of battery.

      (hold <sprite index=123> or <sprite index=124>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 418191228022784
    m_Localized: 'Turbo Turtle activates a limited-range scan that detects Flowers
      through obstacles.

      (<sprite index=36>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 418911813644288
    m_Localized: 'Turbo Turtle drops a mine on the ground, which stuns Flowers on
      contact (up to 5 active mines).

      (<sprite index=35>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 428248883802112
    m_Localized: Poppy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 428426927812608
    m_Localized: Dandelion
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 428524407631872
    m_Localized: White Lily
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 428762589573120
    m_Localized: Cornflower
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 428814393421824
    m_Localized: Clover
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 428924829446144
    m_Localized: Rose
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8495364757544960
    m_Localized: 2D & 3D Artist
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8496045115596800
    m_Localized: Animator
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8498721811357696
    m_Localized: Objectives
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8499963035934720
    m_Localized: As a Flower
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8500286030897152
    m_Localized: As Turbo Turtle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8500909644210176
    m_Localized: The Flowers must run, hide, and use their powers to make Turbo Turtle
      run out of battery!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8501869036724224
    m_Localized: Turbo Turtle must eliminate all the Flowers before its battery drops
      to 0!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8503203353878528
    m_Localized: Energy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8504687399297024
    m_Localized: Revival
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8506246514368512
    m_Localized: As a Flower
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8506458846814208
    m_Localized: As Turbo Turtle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8508129450680320
    m_Localized: Suns collected by the Flowers let them use unique powers! Their
      abilities cost between 1 and 3 Sun-energy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8516727576748032
    m_Localized: With 3 Suns, you can revive an eliminated Flower by approaching
      it and holding <sprite index=35>, which will spend all your Sun-energy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83184034177114112
    m_Localized: '<color=#E4C824>Ability - Dematerialize: <color="Black>3 Suns (<sprite
      index=33>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83182293087969280
    m_Localized: '<color=#FF4C00>Ability - Grappling Hook: <color="Black> 1 Sun (<sprite
      index=33>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83182508167684096
    m_Localized: <color=#FF4C00>Poppy <color=#433F3F>throws a <color=#FF4C00>grappling
      hook <color=#433F3F>in the direction it's facing. If the hook <color=#FF4C00>hits
      an element of the environment<color=#433F3F>, <color=#FF4C00>Poppy<color=#433F3F>
      is <color=#FF4C00>pulled<color=#433F3F> toward it until the hook is released.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83182761520422912
    m_Localized: Passive - Adrenaline
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83183508106534912
    m_Localized: When <color=#FF4C00>Poppy<color=#433F3F> is the <color=#FF4C00>last<color=#433F3F>
      Flower alive, <color=#FF4C00>its speed increases.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83183900311707648
    m_Localized: Agile
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83184493281435648
    m_Localized: <color=#E4C824>Dandelion<color=#433F3F> <color=#E4C824>dematerializes<color=#433F3F>,
      becoming <color=#E4C824>untouchable and faster <color=#433F3F>for a few seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83184530199699456
    m_Localized: <color=#E4C824>Passive - Light as Air
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83185993609142272
    m_Localized: While <color=#E4C824>Dandelion<color=#433F3F> is <color=#E4C824>planted<color=#433F3F>,
      it <color=#E4C824>doesn't appear on Turbo Turtle's scan<color=#433F3F>, but
      the detection sound still triggers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83186216142135296
    m_Localized: Elusive
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83186412213264384
    m_Localized: Ability - Energy Gift <color="Black>(<sprite index=33>)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83187175215882240
    m_Localized: "<color=#95BC5B>White Lily<color=#433F3F> sacrifices all the <color=#95BC5B>Suns
      it holds<color=#433F3F> (1 to 3) \r\nto <color=#95BC5B>give the same amount<color=#433F3F>
      to each of the other Flowers."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83187240990957568
    m_Localized: Passive - Glimmer of Hope
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83187363619823616
    m_Localized: <color=#95BC5B>White Lily<color=#433F3F> doesn't need <color=#95BC5B>any
      Suns to revive<color=#433F3F> allied Flowers. Each time it revives a Flower,
      it gains a <color=#95BC5B>temporary speed boost<color=#433F3F>.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83187554406129664
    m_Localized: Support
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83187853938155520
    m_Localized: '<color=#459FFF>Ability - Force Field: <color="Black>2 Suns (<sprite
      index=33>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83189501028753408
    m_Localized: <color=#459FFF>Cornflower<color=#433F3F> creates a <color=#459FFF>temporary
      force field<color=#433F3F>, <color=#459FFF>protecting it from any outside attack<color=#433F3F>
      while active.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83190282679246848
    m_Localized: <color=#459FFF>Passive - Unbreakable Solidarity
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83190341907013632
    m_Localized: If <color=#459FFF>another Flower<color=#433F3F> is inside the force
      field, it is <color=#459FFF>also protected<color=#433F3F>. The force field
      <color=#459FFF>violently repels Turbo Turtle<color=#433F3F> on contact.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83190435276414976
    m_Localized: Protector
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83190512128647168
    m_Localized: '<color=#AF5E89>Ability - Transplant: <color="Black>3 Suns (<sprite
      index=33>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83191296773873664
    m_Localized: "Si <color=#AF5E89>Tr\xE8fle<color=#433F3F> est <color=#AF5E89>plant\xE9e<color=#433F3F>
      dans le sol, elle peut <color=#AF5E89>\xE9changer de position<color=#433F3F>
      \r\navec une fleur <color=#AF5E89>al\xE9atoire<color=#433F3F> du d\xE9cor."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83191330777096192
    m_Localized: Passive - Stroke of Luck
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83191370237108224
    m_Localized: "When <color=#AF5E89>Clover<color=#433F3F> picks up a Sun, it has
      a <color=#AF5E89>1 in 4 chance \r\nof getting 3 instead<color=#433F3F>."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83191407256035328
    m_Localized: Opportunist
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83191576022245376
    m_Localized: '<color=#6A4B89>Ability - Revival Glyph: <color="Black>3 Suns (<sprite
      index=33>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83192263548362752
    m_Localized: <color=#6A4B89>Rose<color=#433F3F> plants a <color=#6A4B89>seed<color=#433F3F>
      in the ground. If <color=#6A4B89>Rose dies<color=#433F3F>, it is<color=#6A4B89>
      automatically revived at the seed's location<color=#433F3F>, consuming the
      seed in the process (can be destroyed by Turbo Turtle).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83192471648755712
    m_Localized: Passive - Tough as Nails
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83192494444797952
    m_Localized: <color=#6A4B89>Rose<color=#433F3F> isn't <color=#6A4B89>stunned
      by contact with a mine<color=#433F3F> from Turbo Turtle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
