  - m_Id: 83231166376468480
    m_Localized: 'Move (<sprite index=15>)

      Activate ability (<sprite index=33>)

      Hide
      underground (<sprite index=34>)

      Revive an ally (hold <sprite index=35>)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83231166397440000
    m_Localized: 'Move (<sprite index=15>)

      Charge (hold <sprite index=33>
      + <sprite index=15> to aim, then release)

      Bite (<sprite index=34>)

      Mine
      (<sprite index=35>)

      Scan (<sprite index=36>)

      Turbo (hold <sprite
      index=123> or <sprite index=124>)'
